data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of the Spotsylvania County! This captivating 4BD/2.5BA Cape Cod residence, built in 2005, offers an array of outdoor features that elevate the essence of comfortable living. Situated on 1.79 acres with no HOA restrictions, this property provides the perfect blend of privacy and convenience, boasting high-speed fiber optic internet via Verizon Fios—a rare and valuable amenity in the area.  The outdoor oasis beckons with a new 42x16 fiberglass heated saltwater pool, a $95k investment, installed by Marshall Pool's.  The automatic pool cover's hidden track offers safety and peace of mind without being obtrusive. Entertain or unwind on the expansive composite deck, complete with new posts and a sail for shade, offering the perfect vantage point to appreciate the nearly 1 acre fenced rear yard, playground and treehouse! Just around the the side of the house is a private stone patio featuring a built-in wood-burning fireplace.   The main level welcomes you with a versatile floor plan, featuring a first-level bedroom, a charming breakfast nook with a bay window, and new custom remote blinds throughout. The heart of the home is complemented by a shiplap-adorned wall, where the option for a gas fireplace awaits behind the scenes. The kitchen showcases all-new black stainless steel appliances, including an LG Instaview fridge, creating a stylish and functional space for culinary enthusiasts.  The first-level primary bedroom impresses with a cathedral ceiling and ensuite bath offering a stall shower and separate soaking tub, depending on your preference. A flex space just off the kitchen is perfect for a formal dining room, home office or playroom. Laundry and a half bath are conveniently located on the back of the house with access to both the pool deck and garage. The upper level completes the finished living space with an additional 3 bedrooms and a hall bath for guests and family.   On the front porch, you can enjoy views of crepe myrtles and dogwoods thoughtfully added since moving in. The property also includes a 2-car front-load garage and a walkout lower level with over 1,000 square feet of unfinished space that includes a rough-in plumbing.  Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a home that combines modern luxury with the serenity of nature. With easy access to the top rated schools, a wealth of outdoor amenities, and the convenience of high-speed fiber optic internet, this property is a true gem in the market.  Offer deadline is Monday 12/4 at noon!
